metadata.description:
Take a piece of paper, sharpen the pencil and start doodling whatever comes to mind

'Mind scribbles' simulates hand-drawn strokes, with pencil and ink. The colors are inspired by ancient oriental arts. 

- 10 color palettes;
- Margin or no margin;
- There may be a circular pattern in the center or a negative circular space;
- There may be a rectangular pattern in the center or a negative rectangular space;
- Press 's' on live mode to save in PNG hi-res;

April 2022, @gpitombo
